//
// This module provides the core collection types:
// - HashMap: Hash table with separate chaining
// - HashSet: Set implemented via HashMap
// - BTreeMap: Ordered map using B-tree
// - BTreeSet: Ordered set using B-tree
// - VecDeque: Double-ended queue
// - LinkedList: Doubly-linked list
// - BinaryHeap: Priority queue
//
